<anchor id="measurement_8h_1measurement_builder"/> <simplesect kind="par"><title>Detailed Description </title><para>Measurement are send cyclically via LTE to the MQTT broker. the measurement builder is responsible to prepare the measurement JSON string, which contains the measurement data and to clear it after transmission. See also message sequence charts in section <ref refid="_m_s_c_1SectionMeasurement" kindref="member">Measurement</ref>.</para>
</simplesect>
